ycling in the borough. "],"\n",["P",{},"You can use this part of the website to ",["A",{"href":"/recycling-waste-and-bins/garden-waste/garden-waste-sign-up-form/","title":"Garden Waste Sign Up Form"},"sign up for our garden waste collection service"],", ",["A",{"rel":"noopener","href":"/recycling-waste-and-bins/find-my-bin-collection-days/","target":"_blank","title":"Find My Bin Collection Days"},"find your bin day"]," and ",["A",{"href":"/recycling-waste-and-bins/request-a-bin/","title":"Request a Bin"},"request a new/replacement bin"],"."],"\n",["P",{},"Alternatively, you can ",["A",{"rel":"noopener","href":"/media/ptbk0ogl/new_waste_and_recycling_service_guide_march_2024.pdf","target":"_blank","title":"Household Waste And Recycling Service Guide [pdf] 11901KB"},"the download the household waste guide"]," which covers information regarding your waste collections."],"\n",["P",{},"We also provide services for ",["A",{"href":"/recycling-waste-and-bins/large-item-collection/","title":"Large Item Collection"},"large item collections"],", ",["A",{"href":"/recycling-waste-and-bins/commercial-and-hazardous-waste/sharps-syringes-and-clinical-waste/","title":"Sharps, Syringes and Clinical Waste"},"clinical waste collection"]," and ",["A",{"href":"/recycling-waste-and-bins/assisted-collection-help-moving-your-bins/","title":"Assisted Collection - Help Moving Your Bins"},"assisted collections"]," (help with moving your bins)."],"\n",["P",{},"Unsure of how to dispose of your waste? Then ",["A",{"href":"#","title":"How Do I Dispose of?"},"check out our guidance on what you can and can’t recycle"],"."],"\n",["P",{},"If you are a business then ",["A",{"href":"/recycling-waste-and-bins/commercial-and-hazardous-waste/","title":"Commercial and Hazardous Waste"},"view our guidance on commercial and business waste"],"."],"\n            "],"\n        "],"\n    "],"\n\n",["DIV",{"class":"row shFAQ"},"\n    ",["DIV",{"class":"col-md-12"},"\n        \n\n    "],"\n"],"\n\n\n            \n 